<br>
It just doesnt seem to me that it is worth huge sums to me.<br>
<br>
If you wanted to stick with ID4 to have focus for magic/fire/cold you could simply continue to get free mage bracers.  Obviously the stats on the bracers suck...<br>
<br>
If you had one nuke that you favored you could get other crafted 'anger' items for significantly less than what it seems the burners will run.<br>
<br>
