<br>
Also, some of the components are extremely rare (fiery granite, solidified magma). And just look at the stats.<br>
<br>
Item: Ceramic Incense Burner of Ro, MAGIC, Slot: RANGE PRIMARY SECONDARY, STA: 10, WIS: 8, INT: 8, AGI: 12, HP: 65, MANA: 65, SV COLD: 15, Required: L46, Focus: Improved Damage IV, WT: 2.0, Size: SMALL, Classes: ALL, Races: ALL, <br>
<br>
I simply cannot see how this item could go lower then 150k. That's really what the market value of such an item would be. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4356" target="top"><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.gameden.ca/EQ/sig2.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=absolutemaster>Absolute Master</A> at: 4/21/03 10:38:37 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wandork>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Warriors ph34r me!<BR>Gnomercy for Gno-one!</span><br>  Posts: 2080<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/21/03 10:34:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26195.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ceramic Incense Burner of Ro</span><hr size=1> It also works on disease and poison nukes - for which there are no specific anger focus. If you want to focus PR and DR nukes, you have to get one of the all inclusive focus items (ID4, Anger of Solusek, Fury of Solusek).<br>
<br>
Other than a mage bracer, this is the only tradeable ID4 item in the game.<br>
<br>
