<br>
With the rarity of the magma and the quality of the effect (stats suck compared to other elemental trade skill items, but that is another gripe) it is reasonable to price these at least 2x more than an ID3 item. On Terris I will be surprised if they go for under 150k when they finally do hit the bazaar. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=artillis>Artillis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Enjoys Sheep Erotica</span><br>  Posts: 1746<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/21/03 3:24:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26195.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ceramic Incense Burner of Ro</span><hr size=1> Humm I think the MP4 item interests me more, what are stats on those how rare are they on average and such? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=qaman>Qaman</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 2933<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/21/03 3:37:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26195.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ceramic Incense Burner of Ro</span><hr size=1> Not to mention that the pofire pottery item is probaby the easiest one to get the parts for as well. Tier 4 pottery pretty much sucks compared to the rest of the items there.<br>
